author: Yael Halon
title: Newt Gingrich: Italian government didn't realize how dangerous coronavirus outbreak was going to be
description: Former House Speaker Newt Gingrich, who is currently in Italy with his wife, told the "Fox News Rundown" podcast Tuesday that flight connections between Wuhan and Milan may be the source of the early coronavirus outbreak in the European country.
